{"tid":981841,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"熱刺中場迪比利嚟香港體測?傳將體測加盟廣州富力","createTime":"2019-01-14T15:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T19:23:24.000Z","uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3f83225334ab4fa191fc0fa823949676d431a93f","tid":981841,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:12:21.000Z","msg":"效力英超熱刺的31歲比利時中場迪比利，周日在球隊主場迎戰曼聯的賽事中，連18人大軍名單都未有列入，外媒更指他周一早上登上了前赴香港的航班，目前正在來港！到底他為何不出戰曼聯，而要坐飛機來香港呢？ <br />\n<br />\n英國天空體育報道指，迪比利正乘坐前往香港的航班，目的是在明天接受國內中超球會，北京國安安排的體測，未知迪比利來港是為了轉機，還是會在港進行體測，但他離開熱刺轉投中超的可能性已達到99.9%，據報轉會費將達900萬鎊（約9,000萬港元）。 <br />\n<br />\n不過有內媒則指出，迪比利加盟的球會並不是北京國安，而是加盟與香港較近的廣州富力，所以才會來香港體測；又稱迪比利早在月初已確認會轉投中超，但因手續問題才延在本週來港，傳他體測成功後將會簽約。"},{"pid":"ffa223ff7e79a2a4c4966712ddb2555d5b5d1dee","tid":981841,"uid":54524,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:13:11.000Z","msg":"900萬鎊咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db2246636de18cb5b942e93c5555a3fcba732045","tid":981841,"uid":151324,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ffa223ff7e79a2a4c4966712ddb2555d5b5d1dee","tid":981841,"uid":54524,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:13:11.000Z","msg":"900萬鎊咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:17:18.000Z","msg":"平又點 香港買唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de0551a57023370a106645797b580d2b1a0a4b9","tid":981841,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:19:32.000Z","msg":"呢個迪比利幾勁"},{"pid":"e37390d1af375f6e91685a9d44188d23d8ac9538","tid":981841,"uid":8588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ffa223ff7e79a2a4c4966712ddb2555d5b5d1dee","tid":981841,"uid":54524,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:13:11.000Z","msg":"900萬鎊咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:21:31.000Z","msg":"比利時HLN報導，為了感謝大屎忽多年來對俱樂部的貢獻和忠誠，熱刺在收到國安報價後完全沒有還價就同意了這筆轉會。"},{"pid":"a09f87d269fa5fc191ab4720a1eb2a47c1b31028","tid":981841,"uid":8883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db2246636de18cb5b942e93c5555a3fcba732045","tid":981841,"uid":151324,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ffa223ff7e79a2a4c4966712ddb2555d5b5d1dee","tid":981841,"uid":54524,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:13:11.000Z","msg":"900萬鎊咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:17:18.000Z","msg":"平又點 香港買唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:23:51.000Z","msg":"我地起座橋填個海簽n個啦"},{"pid":"27b21283099c1b89deac86b7bddd4fdc81064c8d","tid":981841,"uid":230798,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T16:16:27.000Z","msg":"More detail?幾時到 住邊 想追佢影相<br />\n利申： 比利時粉"},{"pid":"91167c56f613f83ba5ef41568ea09a8e3fdda563","tid":981841,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T17:08:00.000Z","msg":"佢唔係熱加狗主力黎？<br />\n有期係咪佢+Dier 雙防中？<br />\n咁快就無掟企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c1ace5bce1dc915272659b04222943e1e189aa","tid":981841,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T17:24:57.000Z","msg":"點解比利時會出佢唔出尼恩哥蘭?"},{"pid":"88bc6ba1ef87e80682a57e4184e76c7442d423e2","tid":981841,"uid":66433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4c1ace5bce1dc915272659b04222943e1e189aa","tid":981841,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T17:24:57.000Z","msg":"點解比利時會出佢唔出尼恩哥蘭?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T17:48:26.000Z","msg":"尼恩高蘭退出左國家隊啦"},{"pid":"924745a2e1c84eea21aeceff38bf336a22685a19","tid":981841,"uid":34293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"88bc6ba1ef87e80682a57e41